  "title": "Use The Tool!",
  "description": "A simple, light-weight mod that requires the player to use the correct tool to mine a block",
  "body": "<div><center>\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=14n5iB5HeOOhCcT-vwlVCFngG-O-pCPdP\"  alt=\"Use The Tool logo\">\n<h2>\n<b>A simple, light-weight mod that requires the player to use the correct tool to mine a block</b>\n</h2>\n<br>\n<a href=\"\">\n<img alt=\"modrinth\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/modrinth_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/RamCorporation/UseTheTool\">\n<img alt=\"github\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/github_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n<br>\n<img alt=\"fabric\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/supported/fabric_vector.svg\">\n<img alt=\"forge\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/unsupported/forge_vector.svg\">\n\n</center></div>\n\n# TL;DR\n\n---\nPrevents the player from mining a block if the item they are using is not the correct tool for the job.\n\n# Wait... How Do I Get Wood?\n\n---\nSame as before. The Mod only kicks in when a player tries to mine a block with the wrong tool OR tries to break something that should not be broken their fist/random item in hand.\n\n## License\n\n---\nThis project is under an MIT license",
